Class Song

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xbmc.api.object.Song
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, ICoverArt, INamedResource

    public class Song
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICoverArt, INamedResource
    The song class contains everything to know about a song. It's basically a data container with some smallish formatting methods

    Team XBMC
